      "FacilityID": 29274,
      "SummaryText": "This risk management plan is being submitted as a correction and update to the Wyoming Valley Sanitary Authority RMP (EPA Facility ID #1000 0017 4438).  Changes to the plan were necessitated by personnel changes as well as procedural and policy changes.  A voluntary, in-house emergency response team has been disbanded and the facility will now rely on local emergency responders and a private contractor in the event of a response involving 40 CFR Part 68 substances.  A meeting with WVSA Employees, Luzerne County LEPC, local community emergency rescue personnel and the contracted responder was held to communicate new policy and potential risks.  The plan is in effect as of the date of this report."
